---
// About.astro – QuetzalSoftware

const techStack = [
  { name: '.NET', color: 'bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 border-purple-200' },
  { name: 'Laravel', color: 'bg-red-100 text-red-700 border-red-200' },
  { name: 'Vue.js', color: 'bg-green-100 text-green-700 border-green-200' },
  { name: 'Docker', color: 'bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 border-blue-200' },
  { name: 'PostgreSQL', color: 'bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 border-sky-200' },
  { name: 'Astro', color: 'bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 border-orange-200' },
  { name: 'REST APIs', color: 'bg-teal-100 text-teal-700 border-teal-200' },
  { name: 'CI/CD', color: 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 border-gray-200' },
];

const stats = [
  { value: '5+', label: 'Años de experiencia' },
  { value: '30+', label: 'Proyectos entregados' },
  { value: '100%', label: 'Compromiso con el cliente' },
];
---

<section id="nosotros" class="py-24 bg-green-50 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative shape -->
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 bg-green-100 rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/3 blur-2xl opacity-60"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-56 h-56 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/4 blur-2xl opacity-50"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-green-700 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">
        Quiénes somos
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Sobre Nosotros
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Two-column layout -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left column: Text content -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Fundador & Líder técnico</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Giovanni Recinos</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">QuetzalSoftware</strong> es una empresa de desarrollo de software con sede en Guatemala, 
          dirigida por <strong class="text-green-700">Giovanni Recinos</strong>, analista de sistemas y desarrollador con 
          amplia experiencia en la creación de soluciones digitales para el sector empresarial.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Nuestra filosofía se basa en construir <strong class="text-gray-800">ecosistemas digitales robustos</strong> que 
          no solo resuelven el problema de hoy, sino que sientan las bases para el crecimiento del mañana. Utilizamos 
          tecnologías de vanguardia como <strong class="text-gray-800">.NET, Laravel y Vue.js</strong>, combinadas con 
          arquitecturas modernas basadas en <strong class="text-gray-800">Docker y contenedores</strong>, para garantizar 
          la <em>escalabilidad corporativa</em> que tu empresa necesita.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Creemos que el software debe ser una ventaja competitiva, no una carga. Por eso cada proyecto se desarrolla 
          con atención al detalle, código limpio y un compromiso total con la calidad y los tiempos de entrega.
        </p>

        <!-- Tech stack pills -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Stack tecnológico</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {techStack.map((tech) => (
              <span
                class={`inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full border ${tech.color} transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-105`}
              >
                {tech.name}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="pt-2">
          <a
            href="#contacto"
            id="about-cta"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-green-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
          >
            Trabaja con nosotros
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: Visual card -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Main card with stats -->
        <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-green-100 border border-green-100 p-8 overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Top decoration -->
          <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 via-emerald-500 to-teal-400 rounded-t-3xl"></div>

          <!-- Avatar / Illustration -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 pt-2">
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg shadow-green-200">
                <svg class="w-9 h-9 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.982 18.725A7.488 7.488 0 0012 15.75a7.488 7.488 0 00-5.982 2.975m11.963 0a9 9 0 10-11.963 0m11.963 0A8.966 8.966 0 0112 21a8.966 8.966 0 01-5.982-2.275M15 9.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-5 h-5 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white" aria-label="Disponible"></span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-lg">Giovanni Recinos</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Analista de Sistemas & Desarrollador</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-green-600 font-medium mt-0.5">● Disponible para nuevos proyectos</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Stats -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
            {stats.map((stat) => (
              <div class="text-center p-3 rounded-xl bg-green-50 border border-green-100">
                <p class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-green-700">{stat.value}</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 leading-tight">{stat.label}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Values -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            {[
              { icon: '🎯', text: 'Enfoque en resultados empresariales reales' },
              { icon: '🔒', text: 'Arquitecturas seguras y escalables' },
              { icon: '⚡', text: 'Desarrollo ágil con entregas iterativas' },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 transition-colors duration-200">
                <span class="text-xl" aria-hidden="true">{item.icon}</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-700 font-medium">{item.text}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative floating badge -->
        <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-green-100 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-900">Estabilidad</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">& Crecimiento</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
